The '''Clariv Shipyards''' was a [[Shipyard/Legends|shipyard]]. The [[Kerestian/Legends|Kerestian]] [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Milacass]] was the victim of an explosion at the shipyards which resulted in searing to both [[Gender/Legends|his]] [[Eye/Legends|eyes]]. Although his vision returned, Milacass's eyes no longer appeared to have pupils.

